<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4551001>
    dc:description "Fig. 3. Dorsal view of left pectoral-fin spine of (a) holotype (INPA 41133, 36.5 mm SL) and (b) paratype (MZUEL 5925, 20.5 mm SL) of Microglanis maculatus, from ribeirão Pouso Alegre, tributary of rio dos Patos, upper rio Tocantins basin, BarroAlto, Goiás State, Brazil. Scale bar = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4551001/files/figure.png" ;
