<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4551003>
    dc:description "Fig. 4. Type locality of Microglanis maculatus (red circle), ribeirão Pouso Alegre, tributary of rio dos Patos, upper rio Tocantins basin, Barro Alto, Goiás State, Brazil." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4551003/files/figure.png" ;
